name: Take Them Away
Lore: 'During the occupation of Naboo, battle droids were ordered to arrest any Naboo citizens on sight.',
Text: 'USED: Subtract one from a just drawn battle destiny.LOST: During opponent''s control phase, use X Force to ''break cover'' of an opponent''s undercover spy at same site as your battle droid or Neimoidian, where X = spy''s deploy cost.',
